{"word":"παροξύνω","slug":"παροξύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παροξύνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ῠνῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to urge, prick</i> or <i>spur on, stimulate</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to anger, provoke, irritate, exasperate</i>, <el>πατρὸς μὴ π. φρένα</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be provoked</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}